Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:21.69,ED_JP1,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}誰にも気づかれず香る花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.85,0:22:23.90,ED_JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}ちゃんと水を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.00,0:22:26.30,ED_JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}吸って息をして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.60,0:22:31.10,ED_JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}笑ったり泣いたりして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.10,0:22:36.83,ED_JP3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}気づいてよ  嘘の優しさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.45,0:22:39.20,ED_JP3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}見て見ぬフリした
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:43.20,ED_JP3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}ひとり雨宿り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:46.75,ED_JP3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}けど 空に罪はない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:49.20,ED_JP4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}ワタシだけが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:52.40,ED_JP4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}もっている花言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:22:56.75,ED_JP4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}見失い また夢中で探した
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.30,0:23:00.81,ED_JP4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}他の誰かじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.00,0:23:02.60,ED_JP4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}見つけられない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:05.44,ED_JP4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}大事なモノ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:09.85,ED_JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}昨日のワタシと  交わした約束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.00,0:23:14.36,ED_JP3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}思い出し  また明日を探した
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:18.37,ED_JP1,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}花びらが散らぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.40,0:23:23.20,ED_JP1,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}私は私を抱きしめるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:17.45,ED_CHT1,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}过于耀眼的太阳阴影下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:21.69,ED_CHT1,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}我是无人察觉散发芬芳的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.85,0:22:23.90,ED_CHT2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}我竭力地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.00,0:22:26.30,ED_CHT2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}汲取水分呼吸着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.60,0:22:31.10,ED_CHT2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}时而会欢笑时而会哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.10,0:22:36.83,ED_CHT3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}请注意到我  装作不曾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.45,0:22:39.20,ED_CHT3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}看到温柔的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:43.20,ED_CHT3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}独自在躲雨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:46.75,ED_CHT3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}但是 天空并无罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:49.20,ED_CHT4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}将属于我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:52.40,ED_CHT4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}一个人的花语给
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:22:56.75,ED_CHT4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}迷失了 然后便不顾一切找寻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.30,0:23:00.81,ED_CHT4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}这是任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.00,0:23:02.60,ED_CHT4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}都无法发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:05.44,ED_CHT4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}珍贵之物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:09.85,ED_CHT2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}我由此想起了和昨天的自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.00,0:23:14.36,ED_CHT3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}那个约定  明天再次去找寻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:18.37,ED_CHT1,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}为了不让花瓣飘散凋零
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.40,0:23:23.20,ED_CHT1,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}我就此紧紧地拥着自己
